{}

### Get all tastes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tastes/list HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Create a new taste
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tastes/create HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "foodTypeId": 1,
  "name": "Spicy",
  "moneyAdded": 50,
  "remark": "Extra spicy flavor"
}

### Update a taste
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tastes/update HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "foodTypeId": 1,
  "name": "Mild",
  "moneyAdded": 30,
